

Input -> Passing data to the clild 

Child component:
-----------------
step 1 : Child component Define a property with @input decorator 
@input DispalyDetails : boolian 

Parent Template : 
-----------------
<PM-Criteria DispalyDetails = true> binding this to pass data from parent to child 
</PM-Criteria>

Parent component can bind a value, or expression or one of its own properties -> in the above 
example we pass the value 'true' . Instead of true above we can pass pass the parent property 
Parent component:
------------------

IncludeDetails : boolean = true;

<PM-Criteria [DispalyDetails] = 'IncludeDetails'> 
</PM-Criteria>
